data.description: Enjoy lake front living & gorgeous sunsets from your screened patio in this well maintained 2 bdr/2 bath villa with den. Popular Buttonwood floor plan offers generous great room with tray ceiling, open concept dining room & kitchen. Upgrades in kitchen include quartz counters, 42' inch white cabinets, SS appliances, tile backsplash, large pantry. Other wonderful features are: wood plank tile throughout home, plantation shutters on all windows, IMPACT GLASS WINDOWS, tinted windows for energy efficiency, high quality epoxy finish on garage floors & screened patio with paver flooring. Master bedroom has tray ceiling wonderful lake view & huge walk in closet. Full clubhouse amenities: htd resort style pool, fitness center. Close proximity to downtown Tradition shops, restaurants & activities
